    "class": "gps-596220892967928422 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/1wi06b-ei/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=596220892917269094&sectionId=596220892967928422)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzjA58WnwW_text","label":"ggzjA58WnwW_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">A Shepherd —identical to Clove—eating from something called a CalmBowl. But instead of the frantic gulping that killed my parents' dog, this one was... peaceful.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"The rotating blade barrier system doesn't just slow eating. It <strong>completely deactivates the neurological trigger.</strong>\"</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"How is that possible?\"</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"The circular blade channels create three-dimensional barriers that make scooping and gulping physically impossible. Instead of triggering competition panic, it activates natural foraging behavior—like searching for food in nature.\"</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggw_Ra3AKe0_text","label":"ggw_Ra3AKe0_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:32px;\"><strong>The Massacre Happening In Your Kitchen Right Now</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gga3AvmNcLj_text","label":"gga3AvmNcLj_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Dr. Stevens showed me last month's statistics from just her clinic:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">8 dogs admitted with bloat</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">6 died despite surgery</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Average time from eating to death: 47 minutes</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"Every. Fucking. Night,\" she said, tears in her eyes. \"I watch dogs die while owners sob about the slow feeder that 'worked great until tonight.'\"</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"Shepherds are the second highest risk breed. Deep chest cavity. More room for the stomach to flip. <strong>Your parents' dog was a ticking time bomb from the first meal</strong>.\"</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkRAaesqb1_text","label":"ggkRAaesqb1_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:32px;\"><strong>The Special Solution That Actually Works</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPnuwiX-q7_text","label":"ggPnuwiX-q7_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">The CalmBowl's rotating blade barrier system isn't marketing bullshit:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Circular blade</strong> channels make scooping physically impossible</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Triggers natural foraging instinct</strong> instead of competition panic</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Slows eating 15x</strong> from 30 seconds to 8+ minutes eliminating gulping reflex</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Works for all snout shapes</strong> from pugs to collies</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Medical-grade stainless steel</strong> (plastic grows deadly bacteria)</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Approved by veterinarians </strong>who see bloat deaths nightly</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"Zero cases in many years of tracking.\"</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCPGo71nte_text","label":"ggCPGo71nte_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:32px;\"><strong>The Parents Who Almost Shared Our Nightmare</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPj7BwB5Z2_text","label":"ggPj7BwB5Z2_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"Lost my first Shepherd in my arms to bloat. $6,000 surgery failed. When I got another, the emergency vet MANDATED CalmBowl. Said 'I'm not watching you go through that again.' Three years, zero scares. I actually sleep at night.\" - Patricia K., Denver</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"Watched my neighbor's dog die from bloat IN THEIR DRIVEWAY. Couldn't make the 8-minute drive. Bought CalmBowl that night. The difference is insane—from violent gulping to actual chewing. My GSD is 7 now.\" - Michael S., Dallas &nbsp;</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\"I'm an ER vet tech. The bloat deaths I see... it's always 'but we had a slow feeder!' EVERY staff member here uses CalmBowl. It's the ONLY thing that addresses the real cause.\" - Dr. Amanda R., Phoenix</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDktVsFHP2_text","label":"ggDktVsFHP2_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:32px;\"><strong>The 30-Minute Timer Is Already Ticking</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggr5wGArd9g_text","label":"ggr5wGArd9g_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Right now, your dog is either protected or playing Russian roulette.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Those air bubbles don't disappear. They accumulate. Waiting.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">One jump. One roll. One playful moment after dinner.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Then you have 30 minutes and a $5,000 decision.</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">The CalmBowl costs less than 1% of emergency surgery. Less than Clove's cremation. Less than the therapy my parents need.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFOAOhxfLu_text","label":"ggFOAOhxfLu_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Infinitely less than knowing you could have prevented it.</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Waggier makes only 100 per month due to precision manufacturing. They're offering <strong>35% off </strong>because the founder lost his own GSD to bloat—just like Clove.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMLxfEeCrj_text","label":"ggMLxfEeCrj_text","default":"<p><a href=\"https://waggier.com/products/waggier-calmbowl\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#324FE8;font-size:18px;\"><strong><u>Click the button below now to check if Waggier CalmBowl is still available with the special discount!</u></strong></span></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjTxiykrTg_text","label":"ggjTxiykrTg_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:32px;\"><strong>Don't Let Your Parents Bury Their Best Friend</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcveyZky5e_text","label":"ggcveyZky5e_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">I wasn't there when Clove died. I was 40 minutes away in an office, thinking I'd see her that evening.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">My parents held her as she took her last breath. They haven't recovered.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Seven days. That's all we got because I didn't know the difference between slowing eating and stopping air gulping.</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Now you do.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Your dog is depending on you knowing what I didn't.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Don't become the next family in Dr. Stevens' death statistics.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsdxtwS-hV_text","label":"ggsdxtwS-hV_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:32px;\"><strong>Just Want to Share</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggisdAYz8s2_text","label":"ggisdAYz8s2_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">I'm not trying to scare anyone. But if your dog inhales their food, please understand—<strong>every meal could trigger bloat that gives you just 30 minutes to save them.</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">After losing Clove, I've become obsessed with warning other dog parents. Maybe too obsessed. But last week when my coworker mentioned her Lab \"wolfs down dinner,\" I nearly cried.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">I showed her everything Dr. Stevens taught me about the neurological trigger. How tennis balls and maze bowls don't stop the deadly air gulping.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>She got a CalmBowl. Two days later she texted: \"He's actually CHEWING. First time in 3 years.\"</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>That's why I'm sharing this.</strong> Not because I'm selling anything. Because somewhere tonight, another family is watching their dog gulp dinner, not knowing they're 30 minutes from disaster.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggp_2pNoe4K_text","label":"ggp_2pNoe4K_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong>Covered by a 90-Day Money Back Guarantee</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9fNScjolT_text","label":"gg9fNScjolT_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">If the CalmBowl doesn't completely transform your dog's eating, Waggier will refund every penny.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">They're that confident because they know: once you see your dog eating calmly instead of gulping desperately, you'll never go back to regular bowls.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIJ-qubiar_text","label":"ggIJ-qubiar_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:32px;\"><strong>You Have Two Choices</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-9nDusww3_text","label":"gg-9nDusww3_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">You can keep watching your dog inhale their food.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Hope tonight isn't the night their stomach flips.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Pray you'll have more than 30 minutes to save them.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Or you can take action now and eliminate the risk forever.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Don't wait for your seven-day nightmare.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Don't wait for the emergency that changes everything.</span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Clove never got her chance. Your dog still can.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOkJgAH-s-_label","label":"ggOkJgAH-s-_label","default":"<p>Apply Discount &amp; Check Availability</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7zAnQhlOf_text","label":"gg7zAnQhlOf_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\"><i>Click the link above to see if Waggier is still offering a 35% discount and free shipping</i></span></p>"}],
